pageProduct.name: SUP Stress Less 30 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Adaptogenic herbs like Aswagandha for you to keep calm and carry on.

DEAR STRESS. LET'S BREAK UP.
Faced with the mounting pressure of a fast-paced modern life, success can have a downside aka stress. Stress can negatively affect all aspects of life, overall mood, productivity, immunity and energy levels. We can't always break up with the pressure of life, but we can look to nature to have our back and help improve health and productivity..

WHY POP SUP?
SUP contains Ayurvedic medicines which enhance the body's natural adaptation to stress. SUP's powerful blend of traditional Chinese and Ayurvedic herbs and adaptogens help:

- Alleviate stress and mild anxiety
- Calm nerves
- Reduce mental fatigue
- Support a healthy nervous and immune system POPSUP

Size: 30 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Alleviate stress and mild anxiety
• Calm nerves
• Reduce mental fatigue
• Support a healthy nervous and immune system
• Vegan Friendly

Warnings

If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.

Ingredients

Withania somnifera (Ashwagandha) root ext. dry conc. 250mg
Equiv. to Withania somnifera root dry 3g
Scutellaria baicalensis (Skullcap) root ext. dry conc. 15mg
Equiv. to Scutellaria baicalensis root dry 150mg
Eleutherococcus senticosus (Siberian ginseng) root ext. dry conc. 33.3mg
Equiv. to Eleutherococcus senticosus root dry 500mg
Ocimum tenuiflorum (Holy basil) plant ext. dry conc. 15mg
Equiv. to Ocimum tenuiflorum plant dry 150mg

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Gluten

Directions

Adults
POP 1-2 tablets once or twice daily.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
